          "value": "<p>The assassin becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.zJxUflt9np0q4yML]{Invisible} until the end of her next turn or until she Strikes — her favored repositioning trick (she can also cast <em>feather fall</em> and <em>expeditious retreat</em>).</p>"
